    <abstract>
      <t>   This draft defines how to register/retrieve pETR mapping information
   in LISP when the destination is not registered/known to the local
   site and its mapping system (e.g. the destination is an internet/
   external site destination or scale-out end point in backend data
   center networks of AI Infrastructure).


